cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.SI 

The paper discusses the potential impact of Robotics and Artificial Intelligence on employment, which falls under the category of AI and Robotics. Therefore, cs.AI and cs.RO are the most likely categories. The paper also discusses the opinions of experts and non-experts, which could fall under the categories of Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI). Finally, the paper discusses the estimates and predictions made by the experts, which could fall under the category of Machine Learning (cs.LG).
